channel.title: [C4D] Bathroom
channel.description:
WIP btw.
Basically, I got the idea from scoping out new houses in a new neighborhood, and I started drawing the idea a little later. As you can see, I'm still modeling some of it, but this is just the just of it haha. Tell me what you think?
The lighting deffinitially isn't final. The walls/floors/ceiling are gonna be some tiled ceramics or something. Marble counters and bath. That type of things.
